						<p>Śaka 1154 = A.D. 1232.</p>						

						<p>This verse inscription refers to the construction of the well inside the big tank in Iḍattuvaḷi and fixing of the slabs for mounting the pulley, by a Ulakkēḻuḍaiyāṉ.</p>						

